{
  "text": "The final dataset contains 1,936,962 molecular structures. For experiments, we also provide a training, test and scaffold test sets containing 250, 10, and 10 thousand molecules respectively. The scaffold test set contains unique Bemis-Murcko scaffolds [CITATION_1] that were not present in the training and test sets. We use this set to assess how well the model can generate previously unobserved scaffolds. ",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "19424664"
